ICBSettlementGLTransactionDetail is a BusinessClass
	owned by intercobilling
	prefix is ICBSG
	sql name is "ICBSettlementGLTransDetail"
	
	Ontology
		symbolic key is ICBSettlementGLTransactionDetail
		
	Patterns
		implements Archivable

	Persistent Fields
		FinanceEnterpriseGroup
		IntercompanyBillingGroup
		IntercompanyBillingSettlementHeader
		System								is a GeneralLedgerSystemCode
	
	Conditions
		IsPayablesDistribution
			when (GLTransactionDetail.OriginatingTransaction.BusinessClassName 	= "PayablesInvoiceDistribution"
			or    GLTransactionDetail.OriginatingTransaction.BusinessClassName 	= "IntercompanyBillingDocumentDistribution"
			or    (GLTransactionDetail.OriginatingTransaction.BusinessClassName = "CashLedgerGLDistribution"
			and    GLTransactionDetail.FinanceCodeBlock.ToAccountingEntity 		= IntercompanyBillingSettlementHeader.PayablesCompany.GeneralLedgerCompany.AccountingEntity))
			
		IsReceivablesDistribution
			when (GLTransactionDetail.OriginatingTransaction.BusinessClassName 	= "ReceivableGLDistribution"
			or    (GLTransactionDetail.OriginatingTransaction.BusinessClassName = "CashLedgerGLDistribution"
			and    GLTransactionDetail.FinanceCodeBlock.ToAccountingEntity 		= IntercompanyBillingSettlementHeader.ReceivableCompany.GeneralLedgerCompany.AccountingEntity))
	
	Sets
		BySettlementHeader
			Sort Order
				IntercompanyBillingGroup
				IntercompanyBillingSettlementHeader
				GLTransactionDetail
	
	Actions
		Create is a Create Action
			restricted
		
		Delete is a Delete Action
			restricted
			
		Purge is a Purge Action
			restricted
			bypass relational integrity rules
